{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/price_change_plan/","result":{"data":{"zipFile":{"publicURL":"/static/小书匠价格及邀请活动奖励调整说明-2e59d2d9aef02942c44f83ede36a20f3.zip"},"pdfFile":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"小书匠","siteUrl":"http://www.xiaoshujiang.com"}},"storyWriterMarkdown":{"id":"db2d9b5b-9d2a-5cd6-8581-b460fe6b50c1","html":"\n\n\t<div class=\"preview html_preview xsj_export_zip\"><div style=\"overflow: hidden; position: absolute; top: 0; height: 1px; width: auto; padding: 0; border: 0; margin: 0; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: normal;\"><svg><defs id=\"MathJax_SVG_glyphs\"/></svg></div><h2 class=\"xsj_heading_hash xsj_heading xsj_heading_h2\" id=\"e4bbb7e6a0bc_1\"><div class=\"xiaoshujiang_element xsj_anchor\">\n  <a name=\"e4bbb7e6a0bc_1\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"e4bbb7e6a0bc_1\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a><a name=\"价格\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"价格\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a>\n</div>\n<span class=\"xsj_heading_content\">价格</span></h2>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">从 2019 年 11 月 1 日零时起，小书匠会员价格调整，从原来的每年 20 元人民币调整到每年 40 元人民币。其他规则不变，仅支持一年或者两年的套餐。</p>\n<h2 class=\"xsj_heading_hash xsj_heading xsj_heading_h2\" id=\"e98280e8afb7e4bc98e683a0_2\"><div class=\"xiaoshujiang_element xsj_anchor\">\n  <a name=\"e98280e8afb7e4bc98e683a0_2\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"e98280e8afb7e4bc98e683a0_2\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a><a name=\"邀请优惠\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"邀请优惠\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a>\n</div>\n<span class=\"xsj_heading_content\">邀请优惠</span></h2>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">被邀请者会员时长奖励由原来的 100 天改成 365 天。其他优惠规则不变。详细说明可以查看该<a href=\"http://soft.xiaoshujiang.com/blog/user/invitation\" class=\"xsj_link xsj_manu_link\">文档</a></p>\n<h2 class=\"xsj_heading_hash xsj_heading xsj_heading_h2\" id=\"e5ada6e7949fe4bc98e683a0_3\"><div class=\"xiaoshujiang_element xsj_anchor\">\n  <a name=\"e5ada6e7949fe4bc98e683a0_3\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"e5ada6e7949fe4bc98e683a0_3\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a><a name=\"学生优惠\" class=\"blank_anchor_name\"></a><a id=\"学生优惠\" class=\"blank_anchor_id\"></a>\n</div>\n<span class=\"xsj_heading_content\">学生优惠</span></h2>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\">只要使用了带有 edu 域名的邮箱用户，在完成邮箱验证后进行付款，成为小书匠会员后，自动奖励 730 天的会员时长。该优惠不需要邀请码就可以完成，如果同时使用了邀请码和 edu 邮箱，对于被邀请者，奖励时长无法累加，最终时长为 <strong>730</strong> 天，而不是 <s>730 + 365</s>。对于邀请者，用户数奖励统计依然有效。</p>\n<p class=\"xsj_paragraph xsj_paragraph_level_0\"><strong>注: 一定要先验证 edu 邮箱的有效性后，再进行付款才会奖励 730 天会员时长。付完款升级为正式会员后，再进行 edu 邮箱验证将无法获得奖励。</strong></p>\n</div>\n\n","excerpt":"从 2019 年 11 月 1 日零时起，小书匠会员价格调整，从原来的每年 20 元人民币调整到每年 40 元人民币。其他规则不变，仅支持一年或者两年的套餐。\n被邀请者会员时长奖励由原来的 100 天改成 365 天。其他优惠规则不变。详细说明可以查看该文档\n只要使用了带有 ed...","docType":"blogs","title":"小书匠价格及邀请活动奖励调整说明","customCss":"","createDate":"October 31, 2019","updateDate":"October 31, 2019","tags":["价格","邀请","优惠","小书匠"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='300'%3e%3cpath%20d='M354%2011l1%2011-6%2011c-8%2014-8%2013-17%2014l-11%202h-4l-2%209-3%2013-1%204h-11l-13-1-1%204-2%2014-2%209-10%201c-10%201-10%201-9%204l4%2034a667%20667%200%2000-28%203l-6%201v-7l-1%204v4l-14%205-14%205-14%2024-13%2024-18%206a151%20151%200%2000-38%2016l-18%2010-12%2012-14%2013a362%20362%200%2001-61%2021l-16%206v13h200l200-1V0h-46v11'%20fill='%23d3d3d3'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/3fd8b382c890add566330931b8130ae9/31987/cover2.png","srcSet":"/static/3fd8b382c890add566330931b8130ae9/e1953/cover2.png 250w,\n/static/3fd8b382c890add566330931b8130ae9/46604/cover2.png 500w,\n/static/3fd8b382c890add566330931b8130ae9/31987/cover2.png 1000w,\n/static/3fd8b382c890add566330931b8130ae9/a8378/cover2.png 1024w","sizes":"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw